      "part_type": "Hadith",
      "path": "/books/al-kafi:7:3:46:3",
      "relations": null,
      "text": [
        " قَالَ حَدُّ الْيَهُودِيِّ وَ النَّصْرَانِيِّ وَ الْمَمْلُوكِ فِي الْخَمْرِ وَ الْفِرْيَةِ سَوَاءٌ وَ إِنَّمَا صُولِحَ أَهْلُ الذِّمَّةِ عَلَى أَنْ يَشْرَبُوهَا فِي بُيُوتِهِمْ ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "Ali Bin Ibrahim, from Muhammad Bin Isa, from Yunus, from Ibn Muskan, from Abu Baseer who said, ",
          "‘He<sup>asws</sup> said: ‘The Penalty of the Jew, and the Christian, and the owned (slaves) regarding the wine and the fabrication is the same. But rather, it is correct for the <span class=\"iTxt\">Ahl Al-Zimma</span> (people under responsibility) that they can drink it in their houses’."
        ]
      }
    }
